query:
SELECT rl.*, v.registration, c.name as customer_name 
FROM reminderLogs rl
JOIN vehicles v ON rl.vehicleId = v.id
JOIN customers c ON rl.customerId = c.id
WHERE v.registration = 'MM08OZK'
ORDER BY rl.sentAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
